EC50_Qualifier: This qualifier is to be used with the next TID, EC50. If qualifier is =, IC50 result equals to the value in that column; if qualifier is >, EC50 result is greater than that value.
EC50: EC50 value determined using sigmoidal dose response equation
nH: Hill coefficient determined using sigmoidal dose response equation
CellsNucIntensity: Average cell (GFP) intensity under the nuclei mask
